title: New: Jackie & The Stabbs – I'm Not Waiting
body: If you checked out my [Sound of 2012](http://admin.crackintheroad.com/music/13083-sound-of-2012-part-i-josh/) list, you may recognize the vocals on this track as belonging to a certain **Chelsea Burgin**, who also lends her fall-head-over-heels-in-love tone and irresistible charm to Columbus five piece **Jackie & The Stabbs**. _I’m Not Waiting_ is a gorgeous piano ballad, in a similar vein to the likes of **Feist** and **Regina Spektor**, with **Chelsea’s** stunning vocals backed up by an equally bewitching instrumental section.
